---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to content</a>
    <Header />

    <main id="main">

      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="eyebrow">DevOps &amp; SRE &middot; Canada &middot; $1,500 flat</p>
          <h1>You need Canadian experience to get hired.<br />You need to be hired to get experience.<br /><span class="acc">We break that loop.</span></h1>
          <p class="sub">Two months of real DevOps or SRE work. Real code, real infrastructure, real GitHub history. Then we carry you all the way to a stable job.</p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a href="https://cal.com/yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               data-cal-link="yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call"
               data-cal-namespace="discovery-call"
               data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
               class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Book your enrollment call <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
          </div>
          <p class="fine">30-minute call &middot; No deposit on the call &middot; Canada only</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- WHAT IT IS -->
      <section id="what" class="section alt">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>What you actually do</h2>
          <p class="lead">You are not watching videos. You are not doing tutorials. You are doing real work — the same work Canadian DevOps and SRE engineers do every day at their jobs.</p>

          <div class="two-col">
            <div class="col-block">
              <div class="col-label">DevOps track</div>
              <p>You build CI/CD pipelines. You manage cloud infrastructure. You fix security issues in containers. Your code gets reviewed and merged — the same way it would at any Canadian tech company.</p>
              <div class="tools">AWS &middot; Terraform &middot; GitHub Actions &middot; Kubernetes &middot; Docker</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-block">
              <div class="col-label">SRE track</div>
              <p>You keep systems running. You monitor production health, respond to incidents, write runbooks, and build alerting. Real infrastructure, real consequences if something breaks.</p>
              <div class="tools">AWS &middot; Kubernetes &middot; Prometheus &middot; Grafana &middot; PagerDuty</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="proof-line">
            Every task you complete is a real GitHub contribution. Every merged PR is a real resume bullet. Hiring managers can see it — because it is real.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- JOURNEY -->
      <section id="journey" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>From joining to stable job — every step</h2>
          <p class="lead">Nothing hidden. Nothing left to figure out on your own. Here is exactly what happens.</p>

          <div class="journey">
            <div class="phase-label">Getting the experience</div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">01</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">You join and get your first task</div>
                <div class="jd">Day one: you are assigned to a track and given real work to do. Not a tutorial. A task with acceptance criteria and a reviewer.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">02</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">You work for two months</div>
                <div class="jd">Real tickets. Real code reviews. Real infrastructure. Everything you ship goes on your GitHub, permanently.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="phase-label" style="margin-top: 32px;">Using that experience to get hired</div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">03</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Resume built from your actual work</div>
                <div class="jd">We take every task you shipped and turn it into a resume bullet. Not a description of what Yarova is — a record of what you built.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">04</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Interview prep before every interview</div>
                <div class="jd">You book an interview. We connect before it. We run the exact format that company uses. Every interview gets its own prep session.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">05</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Background check — handled</div>
                <div class="jd">When an offer arrives, we walk you through exactly how to document your Yarova work so it passes a background check cleanly. No ambiguity.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">06</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Day before your first day — prepped</div>
                <div class="jd">We run through what to expect, what to ask, and what to avoid in week one. You walk in ready.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep">
              <div class="jn">07</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Probation check-ins at 30, 60, 90 days</div>
                <div class="jd">We check in three times. We help you navigate anything that feels unclear. We confirm you are on track to clear probation.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="jstep done">
              <div class="jn">&#10003;</div>
              <div class="jbody">
                <div class="jt">Probation cleared. You are stable.</div>
                <div class="jd">That is the finish line. Not a job offer — a stable job past probation. That is what Yarova means by placed.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- PRICING -->
      <section id="pricing" class="section alt">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <h2>One price. No surprises.</h2>

          <div class="price-card">
            <div class="price-top">
              <div class="price-num">$1,500 <span class="ccy">CAD</span></div>
              <div class="price-when">One-time &middot; paid before day one</div>
            </div>

            <ul class="incl">
              <li>Two months of real DevOps or SRE work</li>
              <li>Resume built from your actual ticket history</li>
              <li>Interview prep before every interview you book</li>
              <li>Background check documentation and prep</li>
              <li>Day-one prep call</li>
              <li>Probation check-ins at 30, 60, and 90 days</li>
              <li class="guarantee">Not placed? Re-enroll in the next batch, free. Until you are placed.</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="https://cal.com/yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               data-cal-link="yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call"
               data-cal-namespace="discovery-call"
               data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
               class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Book your enrollment call <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>

            <p class="not-incl">Not included: a guaranteed employer, cloud-provider credits (~$50 over the program), placement outside Canada.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FINAL CTA -->
      <section id="cta-final" class="cta-final">
        <div class="container narrow" style="text-align: center;">
          <h2>Book a 30-minute call.<br />Join or don&rsquo;t.<br /><span class="acc2">No pressure either way.</span></h2>
          <p>We will tell you which track fits your background, when the next batch starts, and what day one looks like. No deposit on the call.</p>
          <div class="actions" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="https://cal.com/yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               data-cal-link="yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call"
               data-cal-namespace="discovery-call"
               data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
               class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Book the enrollment call <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
            <a href="mailto:hello@yarova.ca" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);">Email us instead</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />

    <!-- Floating actions -->
    <div class="floating-actions" aria-label="Quick contact">
      <a class="fa-btn wa" href="https://wa.me/16047197918?text=Hi%20Yarova%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20learn%20more." target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="WhatsApp">
        <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19.05 4.91A9.82 9.82 0 0 0 12.04 2c-5.46 0-9.91 4.45-9.91 9.91 0 1.75.46 3.46 1.32 4.96L2.05 22l5.25-1.38c1.45.79 3.08 1.21 4.74 1.21 5.46 0 9.91-4.45 9.91-9.91 0-2.65-1.03-5.14-2.9-7.01Zm-7.01 15.24c-1.48 0-2.94-.4-4.21-1.15l-.3-.18-3.12.82.83-3.04-.2-.31a8.26 8.26 0 0 1-1.26-4.38c0-4.54 3.7-8.24 8.24-8.24a8.18 8.18 0 0 1 8.24 8.24c.01 4.54-3.69 8.24-8.22 8.24Zm4.52-6.16c-.25-.12-1.47-.72-1.69-.81-.23-.08-.39-.12-.56.12s-.64.81-.78.97c-.14.17-.29.19-.54.06-.25-.12-1.05-.39-1.99-1.23-.74-.66-1.23-1.47-1.38-1.72-.14-.25-.02-.38.11-.51.11-.11.25-.29.37-.43.12-.14.16-.25.25-.41.08-.17.04-.31-.02-.43-.06-.12-.56-1.34-.76-1.84-.2-.48-.4-.42-.56-.43-.14-.01-.31-.01-.48-.01-.17 0-.43.06-.66.31-.23.25-.86.85-.86 2.07s.89 2.4 1.01 2.56c.12.17 1.75 2.67 4.23 3.74.59.26 1.05.41 1.41.52.59.19 1.13.16 1.56.1.48-.07 1.47-.6 1.67-1.18.21-.58.21-1.07.14-1.18-.05-.11-.21-.17-.45-.29Z"/></svg></span>
        <span class="lbl">WhatsApp</span>
      </a>
      <a class="fa-btn cal" href="https://cal.com/yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         data-cal-link="yarova-fxqeea/discovery-call"
         data-cal-namespace="discovery-call"
         data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
         aria-label="Book a call">
        <span class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M16 3v4M8 3v4M3 10h18"/></svg></span>
        <span class="lbl">Book a call</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Cal.com -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
      (function (C, A, L) { let p = function (a, ar) { a.q.push(ar); }; let d = C.document; C.Cal = C.Cal || function () { let cal = C.Cal; let ar = arguments; if (!cal.loaded) { cal.ns = {}; cal.q = cal.q || []; d.head.appendChild(d.createElement("script")).src = A; cal.loaded = true; } if (ar[0] === L) { const api = function () { p(api, arguments); }; const namespace = ar[1]; api.q = api.q || []; if(typeof namespace === "string"){cal.ns[namespace] = cal.ns[namespace] || api; p(cal.ns[namespace], ar); p(cal, ["initNamespace", namespace]);} else p(cal, ar); return;} p(cal, ar); }; })(window, "https://app.cal.com/embed/embed.js", "Cal");
      Cal("init", "discovery-call", {origin:"https://cal.com"});
      Cal.ns["discovery-call"]("ui", {hideEventTypeDetails:false, layout:"month_view", styles:{branding:{brandColor:"#B45309"}}});
    </script>

    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { html { scroll-behavior: auto; } * { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; } }

      a { color: var(--color-amber-hover); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { color: var(--color-amber-press); }
      a:focus-visible { outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(217,119,6,.28); border-radius: 4px; }
      .skip { position: absolute; left: -9999px; top: 8px; background: var(--color-black); color: white; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; z-index: 999; }
      .skip:focus { left: 12px; }

      .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }
      .container.narrow { max-width: 680px; }
      .section { padding: 96px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .section.alt { background: var(--bg-secondary); }

      h1, h2, h3 { font-family: var(--font-sans); margin: 0; color: var(--fg-1); letter-spacing: -.025em; }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 72px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -.035em; }
      h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; }
      p { margin: 0; color: var(--fg-2); line-height: 1.65; }
      .lead { font-size: 18px; color: var(--fg-2); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 680px; margin-top: 20px; }

      .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid transparent; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 120ms ease, background 150ms; text-decoration: none; }
      .btn-lg { padding: 18px 30px; font-size: 16px; }
      .btn-amber { background: var(--color-amber-hover); color: white; box-shadow: 0 8px 22px -10px rgba(217,119,6,.55); }
      .btn-amber:hover { background: var(--color-amber-press); color: white; transform: translateY(-1px); }
      .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg-1); border-color: var(--border); }
      .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--fg-1); border-color: var(--fg-1); }
      .btn .arrow { transition: transform 180ms ease; display: inline-block; }
      .btn:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }

      /* Hero */
      .hero { padding: 88px 0 80px; }
      .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--fg-3); margin-bottom: 32px; }
      .hero h1 { max-width: 960px; }
      .hero h1 .acc { color: var(--color-amber-hover); }
      .sub { font-size: 19px; color: var(--fg-2); margin-top: 28px; max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.55; }
      .actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; margin-top: 36px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .fine { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--fg-3); margin-top: 14px; }

      /* What it is */
      .two-col { margin-top: 48px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
      .col-block { background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px; }
      .col-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--color-amber-hover); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .col-block p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; }
      .tools { margin-top: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-3); letter-spacing: .06em; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .proof-line { margin-top: 36px; padding: 24px 28px; background: var(--color-black); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
      @media (max-width: 700px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

      /* Journey */
      .journey { margin-top: 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
      .phase-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--color-amber-hover); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 8px; }
      .jstep { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 44px 1fr; gap: 20px; background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 22px 24px; align-items: start; }
      .jstep.done { background: var(--color-black); }
      .jstep.done .jn { color: var(--color-amber); }
      .jstep.done .jt { color: white; }
      .jstep.done .jd { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }
      .jn { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-amber-hover); padding-top: 3px; }
      .jt { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--fg-1); margin-bottom: 6px; }
      .jd { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-2); line-height: 1.6; }
      @media (max-width: 600px) { .jstep { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .jn { padding: 0; } }

      /* Pricing */
      .price-card { margin-top: 40px; background: var(--color-black); border-radius: 16px; padding: 44px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
      .price-card::before { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(217,119,6,.18), transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
      .price-top { position: relative; margin-bottom: 32px; }
      .price-num { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 700; color: white; letter-spacing: -.04em; line-height: 1; }
      .price-num .ccy { font-size: 20px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); font-weight: 500; }
      .price-when { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); margin-top: 8px; }
      .incl { margin: 0 0 28px; padding: 0; list-style: none; position: relative; }
      .incl li { padding: 12px 0 12px 28px; position: relative; font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); line-height: 1.5; }
      .incl li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .incl li::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 12px; color: var(--color-amber); font-weight: 700; }
      .incl li.guarantee { color: var(--color-amber); font-weight: 600; }
      .incl li.guarantee::before { content: "★"; }
      .price-card .btn { position: relative; }
      .not-incl { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); line-height: 1.55; position: relative; }

      /* Final CTA */
      .cta-final { background: var(--color-black); color: white; padding: 96px 0; }
      .cta-final h2 { color: white; font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 56px); }
      .cta-final .acc2 { color: var(--color-amber); font-style: normal; }
      .cta-final p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

      /* Floating actions */
      .floating-actions { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 22px; z-index: 55; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
      .fa-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: white; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 120ms ease; box-shadow: 0 8px 22px -8px rgba(0,0,0,.35); }
      .fa-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); color: white; }
      .fa-btn.wa { background: #25D366; }
      .fa-btn.cal { background: var(--color-black); }
      .fa-btn .ic { width: 18px; height: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
      .fa-btn .ic svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
      @media (max-width: 640px) { .fa-btn .lbl { display: none; } .fa-btn { padding: 14px; } }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
